  "instructions": [
    "Shred the cabbage into fine strands and place in a large bowl.",
    "Drizzle sunflower oil over the cabbage and toss to coat evenly.",
    "Add lemon juice, apple cider vinegar, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper and mix thoroughly.",
    "Stir in chopped dill until well distributed.",
    "Cover the bowl and refrigerate for 20 minutes to let flavors meld.",
    "Serve chilled as a crisp, smoky salad."
